snippet.title: Gimme A Break - [Task 2, Act 3] - Adding Simple Fractions
snippet.description: https://tapintoteenminds.com In Task 2, Act 3 of this 3 act math task, students will see how many pieces of a whole 1/2 + 1/4 + 1 + 1/2 of a KitKat add up to.
